  "None suggested yet": "Belum ada cadangan",
  "After the AI responds, a separate quiet API call generates the tracker JSON independently. Expect ~250–300s total per message (narrative + wait + tracker).": "Selepas AI menjawab, panggilan senyap menjana JSON. ~250–300s/mesej.",
  "✓ Single API call — typically ~100–120s total": "✓ Satu panggilan API — ~100–120s",
  "✓ No profile switching — eliminates message deletion risk": "✓ Tanpa tukar profil — tiada risiko",
  "✓ AI has full narrative context for accurate tracking": "✓ AI mempunyai konteks penuh",
  "✓ 2–3× faster than Separate mode in practice": "✓ 2–3× lebih pantas dari Berasingan",
  "✗ Uses tokens from the main response budget (~1,700 tokens for tracker)": "✗ Menggunakan token dari bajet utama (~1,700)",
  "✗ May slightly reduce narrative length on token-limited models": "✗ Mungkin sedikit memendekkan naratif",
