  "✗ Two API calls per message — 2–3× slower than Together mode": "✗ Dua panggilan API — 2–3× lebih perlahan",
  "✗ ~12s dead time between calls (chat save + preset switching)": "✗ ~12s masa menunggu",
  "✗ Tracker prompt is ~10K+ tokens at 8 context msgs — reduce to 3–4 for speed": "✗ Prompt ~10K+ pada 8 mesej — kurangkan ke 3–4",
  "✗ Profile switching can cause message deletion (race condition with other extensions)": "✗ Pertukaran profil mungkin memadamkan mesej",
  "✗ Embeds previous snapshot into narrative call (~1.9K tokens) unless Embed snapshots = 0": "✗ Membenamkan snapshot sebelumnya (~1.9K) melainkan = 0",
  "How many recent messages to include when generating tracker updates.": "Berapa mesej terkini untuk disertakan.",
  "Separate mode only — Together mode uses ST's full context automatically.": "Mod Berasingan sahaja — Bersama guna konteks ST.",
  "Fastest. Good for simple 1-on-1 scenes (~5K token prompt)": "Terpantas. Untuk adegan 1-lawan-1 (~5K)",
  "Balanced. Recommended for most scenes (~8–12K tokens)": "Seimbang. Untuk kebanyakan (~8–12K)",
  "Better continuity for complex multi-character scenes (~12–20K tokens)": "Kesinambungan lebih baik untuk adegan kompleks (~12–20K)",
  "Maximum context but significantly slower and more expensive": "Konteks maksimum tetapi lebih perlahan dan mahal",
  "This is the biggest factor in Separate mode speed. At 8 msgs your tracker prompt is ~10K tokens — doubling roughly doubles generation time. Lower values (3–4) can cut tracker time by 40–60%.": "Faktor terbesar. 8 mesej ~10K — menggandakan masa. 3–4 mengurangkan 40–60%.",
  "Separate mode only.": "Mod Berasingan sahaja.",
  "How many times to retry if the tracker API call returns invalid JSON.": "Berapa kali cuba semula jika JSON tidak sah.",
  "Built-in preset: temp=0.6, top_p=0.95, freq_pen=0.15, max_tokens=4096. Optimized for structured JSON output on GLM-5.": "Pratetap: temp=0.6, top_p=0.95, freq_pen=0.15, max_tokens=4096. Untuk JSON di GLM-5.",
  "Embed recent scene snapshots into the narrative conversation context so the AI can reference tracker state while writing. Only applies in Separate mode. The tracker's own API call always receives the previous snapshot regardless of this setting.": "Membenamkan snapshot ke konteks. Berasingan sahaja. Penjejak sentiasa menerima sebelumnya.",
  "Each embedded snapshot adds ~1.9K tokens to your narrative prompt. Set to 0 to eliminate this overhead — the tracker API call still receives previous state independently. Set to 1 for narrative continuity (AI remembers scene details). Values above 1 are rarely beneficial.": "Setiap snapshot +~1.9K. 0 untuk hapus. 1 untuk kesinambungan. Atas 1 jarang berguna.",
  "Injected as invisible context — AI treats it as authoritative background info. Best for continuity without polluting the conversation.": "Disuntik sebagai konteks tak terlihat — maklumat berwibawa.",
